ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA
A SkillRunner interface defines invoke(inputs, worktree) -> output and captures skill repo+version identity. A stub runner implements it for tests. The chosen I/O contract is documented in the bead before EXECUTE. Interface is unit tested via the stub.

